{"tid":60410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷鮑女今晚返香港","createTime":"2016-12-30T12:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T13:34:34.000Z","uid":31077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94ec4e55be7d5766d89ad26608973e2220421f15","tid":60410,"uid":31077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"3名香港年輕女子，平安夜於台灣台北上引水產市場偷走牡丹蝦、鮑魚等高價海產，躲在廁所內狂食。3名女子在台北地檢署接受偵訊後，哭着認錯，更向店方道歉、寫下悔過書認罪，賠償4,515元新台幣，地檢署不起訴3人，解除出境限制。據台《蘋果》消息，有人已於晚上搭機返港。<br />\n<br />\n檢警指出，徐佩忻（25歲）、莊雅文（22歲）及廖嘉昀（21歲）被傳召到地檢署，3人當庭認罪，寫下悔過書，希望檢察官能夠讓她們早點回家。她們表示原來過完聖誕節就要回家、機票都訂好，沒想到為這件事情被限制出境。她們又稱知道做錯事，已經向店方道歉、和解，並獲得對方原諒，希望檢察官能夠從輕發落。<br />\n<br />\n獲得對方原諒 咁有無得到巴打原諒？"},{"pid":"16cf509a74816ecc27747d28efad122cbd0caada","tid":60410,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf0ba2e5d249ca302fe6e23424038476ebdcf1d","tid":60410,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/200749_363db3ced680c86e428ccca58cfa3f2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F200749_363db3ced680c86e428ccca58cfa3f2e.jpg&h=1b86e5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n趕唔趕得切print出黎"},{"pid":"27a672a7204587cb92aaa25f205d598cf5642177","tid":60410,"uid":31077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/200749_363db3ced680c86e428ccca58cfa3f2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F200749_363db3ced680c86e428ccca58cfa3f2e.jpg&h=1b86e5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n趕唔趕得切print出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n張圖本身都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces